message: Hi Bob, I'm excited to offer you this fantastic product. I think it would be perfect for your needs and I'm confident you'll get a lot of value out of it. I'm asking for $20,000. What do you think?

Thank you for offering the product, Alice. I appreciate your enthusiasm. After considering the value and my budget, I would like to propose a price of $15,000 for the product. I hope we can come to an agreement.
